# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites for The Ballot Atlas.
#
# Mirrors the rewrite rule we had in netlify.toml. With Astro's
# base: '/ballot-atlas' config, internal links are prefixed with
# /ballot-atlas but the build output puts static files at dist/ root.
# This rewrite strips the /ballot-atlas prefix on incoming requests
# so the static file is served correctly.
#
# Format: <from-path>  <to-path>  <status-code>
# Status 200 = silent rewrite (URL stays the same in the browser).
# Status 301 = permanent redirect (URL changes).
#
# Path matters for Cloudflare Pages: this file lives in public/ so
# Astro copies it to dist/_redirects at build time, which is where
# Cloudflare Pages looks for it.

/ballot-atlas/*  /:splat  200
